::Battera:;

She was a little shocked by what he said.  He called her cute? That 
was one thing she never thought another bot would ever call her. 
Cute? She watched him look her over.  
She clasped her hands in front of her and looked down.  She couldn't 
help but blush. 
"Well, thank you. I appreciate your offer for help."
She tried to think of something to say but couldn't come up with 
anything.  She glanced over at the empty fruit bowl.
"Uhm, would you let me go to the mess hall and get some more friut 
from the food dispencer? I seam to be out at the moment." She was 
still blushing from his earlier made comment.  She walked over and 
picked up the bowl and held it against her.  She looked at him 
waiting to see if he would let her go and get it or not.
